description: Experience the best of city living in this stunning duplex condominium conveniently located in the central SB. Constructed in 2013, it is one of 7 units in this well-appointed, pet-friendly, and professionally managed building. This generously proportioned (1,965 SF) 3-bdrm, 3-bath condo with a flexible layout and 2 deeded parking spaces offers the feel of a single-family residence with a private entrance off its rear deck/yard and parking area. The main level, with its superb open layout, including tray ceilings, custom molding, natural hdwd floors, a gas FP, a sun-filled chef's kitchen equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, and granite countertops with a Calcutta backsplash,2 spacious bdrms, 2 full baths, with one being en-suite w/steam shower. The lower level, featuring full-size windows and high ceilings, houses a vast en-suite bedroom that is large enough for a sitting area and a home office. It's a well-maintained unit with numerous updates and plenty of storage.
